text:
Nfufu～
Homemade lunches are always good, but～

Eatin' lunch from th' station
on train as it's shakin' along is also great.

Right!? Picking them out is also fun!
Everyone's look so tasty!

Kiriko, this fried shrimp is somethin' special.
Want one～?

Fufu...
Then... Have some of mine...

Nfufu～ This also looks scrumptious～
Hey hey, Mamimi, won't you eat too?

You don't have to tell me,
I'm already eating anyway.

Fufu.
Is the scenery through the window to you liking, Mamimi?

Not in particular or anything...
Well, sometimes this sort of thing ....
